<i><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://elibrary.wayne.edu/search~S47?/hB446+P27/hb446+p27/-15%2C-1%2C0%2CE/frameset&amp;FF=hb44&amp;1%2C1%2C">An analytical study of the development of major concepts of causality in philosophy</a></i> <span style="font-size:97%;">(1979)</span>
